name: American Airlines 777-323ER [N725AN] Delivery Flight from Paine Field
description:
LONG VERSION HERE: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JrM8-iOcv-g

This is the delivery flight of American Airlines' 9th Boeing 777-300ER departing Paine Field (KPAE/PAE) for Dallas Fort-Worth International Airport. The video features the taxi, engine start, and takeoff. It was very foggy as you can see in the video, so the quality may not be great. I also met a fellow spotter that day, CphSpotting! Check out his video of this bird here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hVOEyn1rcws

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
